unpublishedAction.name: retainUBOEntitiesInKey

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
			const retain_keyPersonData = appsmith.store.keyPersonData
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_BUSINESS_NAME = Input1.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_HOLD_PERC =Number(Input8.text).toString()
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_CONST_TYPE = Input2.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ISLISTED =Checkbox1.isChecked
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_REG_NO = Input7.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_REG_NAME =Input4.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_REG_PLACE =Input3.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_REG_COUNTRY =Select1.selectedOptionValue
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_TAX_RESID_COUNTRY=Select2.selectedOptionValue
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_TAX_ID =Input5.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_TAX_ACCOUNT_NO =Input6.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ADDRESS_LINE1 =Input9.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ADDRESS_LINE2 =Input10.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_CITY =Input11.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_DISTRICT =Input12.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_STATE =Input13.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_ZIP =Input14.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_UBO_ENTITY_COUNTRY =vayEntityUboAddCountrySelect.selectedOptionValue
		return retain_keyPersonData
	}
